content: Wont even load. Just shows a grey fuzzy screen!

Seems to only have 4 songs which isn't very much for a paid app. My son 
really enjoys the songs and interactions with the video. Just gets done 
fast after going thru the 4 songs. Needs more songs and would be a 5.
It's a wonderful game for kids!
My little sister had a blast playing this app! The cute interactions with Beat bugs and singing to the Beatles kept her hooked for hours!
